      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TARAWI THERESE (4) has a superb record at this track and trip, unbeaten so far from six starts. Missed the frame latest (26.05) when fourth over 460m at Warragul in a Mix 3/4. Appeals as a leading chance in this. SUMMER KOBIE (2) found the going tougher last start when finishing 6th over 450m at Ballarat. Scored at Ballarat in weaker company the previous run. Can figure in the finish. FLAMING FOX (1) filled a minor placing last start at this track behind Carry On Maci (16.57) in a Special conditions race. Solid formlines coming through his last run. Expected to be in the finish again. CHAVERO (7) shapes well for this after an enormous 22.42 win latest. One of the chances.",
